{"tid":789924,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"中森明菜疑健康惡化：好想再見大家 但冇可能","createTime":"2018-08-22T15:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T11:36:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"83377086abc982bf39da77f8a192323122624626","tid":789924,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:04:04.000Z","msg":"現年53歲嘅日本一代歌姬中森明菜，多年前開始以健康理由停工，前年年底佢決定再搞Dinner Show重踏舞台，現時佢亦主要靠Dinner Show，同埋不定期發行嘅歌迷會會報同fans溝通。<br />\n<br />\n不過近期嘅會報，已經冇中森明菜近照，連頁數都越嚟越少，有一位女歌迷更指於8月上旬發行嘅會報，明菜嘅親筆留言好令人擔心，留言話：「好寂寞，好想再見大家，但應該冇可能。」該歌迷話去年呢個時間已經有年底Dinner Show嘅報名資料，不過今次新嘅會報卻隻字不提，估計係中森明菜健康惡化，今年冇可能再搞Dinner Show見粉絲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/230342_1870033a9035c5e3f7c99d57cbdf1090.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F230342_1870033a9035c5e3f7c99d57cbdf1090.png&h=58e06a68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180822/58593375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180822%2F58593375&d=wVF4sxI16Ui%2FQc7GR08yLZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e6aeda4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180822%2F58593375&h=2dfdeb71\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180822/58593375</a>"},{"pid":"52ca3f7d8439b7937c5417f23127d549642b37ec","tid":789924,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"老閪"},{"pid":"8eef3b4084f0664e4152aa70857ef00a5a004358","tid":789924,"uid":140802,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T15:09:50.000Z","msg":"一代傳奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bd01ce9c1a85396a6abb681366bb515d004fc9","tid":789924,"uid":77959,"like":0,"disl